 "_comment": [
  "Level tables for the 8 offline-reward runes (OfflineRewardGoldPercent /",
  "OfflineRewardExpPercent stat rows) plus the Rune of Repose (11001) that unlocks offline",
  "rewards at all. Source: TBH wiki. Narrow, targeted extraction for idleInfo only.",
  "",
  "UNITS — v is in PERCENT, converted via /100 in insights::idle_info (v=100 => +100% => x1.0",
  "bonus fraction). Evidence this is /100 not /1000: the stat is literally named",
  "\"OfflineRewardGoldPercent\" (the \"Percent\" suffix means v is already a percent value), and",
  "v=100 uniform per level reads as +100%/level for a dedicated offline-reward rune (max 3-5",
  "levels each), a normal idle-game magnitude. Contrast combat runes like AllHeroAttackSpeed",
  "v=10 (no \"Percent\" suffix, small per-mille buff) — a different stat family with a different",
  "scale. An automated audit flagged /100 as a possible 10x error; the \"Percent\" stat name is",
  "the counter-evidence. STILL not confirmed by a live reading (offline reward is not a combat",
  "stat, so it is absent from FINAL_STATS / the modifier manager). Full confirmation would need",
  "comparing a real pending offline-reward gold amount against this table x (1 + sum(v)/100)."
 ],
